nodes.text: Yuleph Phan was a male Twi'lek Pilgrim who lived on Tython during the Cold War between the Sith Empire and the Galactic Republic.

A Twi'lek male, Yuleph Phan was one of many Pilgrims who followed Matriarch Kolovish to the planet Tython in the aftermath of the Great Galactic War. Assisting in the establishment of Kalikori village, Phan was appointed as the Master of Rituals.
